# Client environment variables. Must be VITE_-prefixed to reach the browser, and are
# baked in at BUILD time (vite build), not at runtime.
#
# In production the client is built and served by the server (single origin), so there
# is NO API base URL to set — the app calls relative /api paths on its own origin.
#
# These are optional (Sentry disabled if unset). To enable in the Docker build, pass
# them as build args (see DEPLOYMENT.md) since client/.env is not copied into the image.

VITE_SENTRY_DSN=""
VITE_SENTRY_ENVIRONMENT="development"
